{"tid":2022719,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［拎完錢會炒人好抵wor]保就業計劃下 如果5人公司拎4萬補貼後發現炒左2個人 政府係會罰佢$1600！！！","createTime":"2020-05-18T13:04:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-19T01:41:43.000Z","uid":22556,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"941502999a8daff728e444feaa384fd1c6874a34","tid":2022719,"uid":22556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-18T13:04:28.000Z","msg":"創新辦總監馮程淑儀舉例，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">若公司人數是 5 人，6 月時公司人數比 3 月少 2 人，40% 的僱員減幅會乘以 4 萬元補貼額，再乘罰款百分率 10%，則被罰 1,600 元</span></span></strong>；至於較大規模、有 500 名員工的公司，每月獲取 500 萬元補貼，如在 6 至 8 月減少五分一人手，按照罰款百分率 80% 計算，最終會被罰款 40 萬。另外，如果僱主在補貼期間未有把領取的當月補貼，全數用於同一月份工資，政府亦會取回未有用於支付工資的補貼額。<br />\n<br />\n他又說，若罰則「太辣」，有些小企業會寧願不申請，故要在罰則及計劃目標中取的平衡。另外，馮程淑儀亦承認計劃無辦法阻止僱主減薪，但認為「至少幫佢（僱員）補住份工」。<br />\n<br />\n詳情 ：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/society/%E4%BF%9D%E5%B0%B1%E6%A5%AD%E8%A8%88%E5%8A%83-%E5%90%A6%E8%AA%8D%E7%BD%B0%E5%89%87%E6%AC%A0%E9%98%BB%E5%9A%87%E6%80%A7-%E7%BE%85%E8%87%B4%E5%85%89-%E8%8B%A5-%E5%A4%AA%E8%BE%A3-%E5%B0%8F%E4%BC%81%E5%AF%A7%E9%A1%98%E4%B8%8D%E7%94%B3%E8%AB%8B/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E4%25BF%259D%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-%25E5%2590%25A6%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%25BD%25B0%25E5%2589%2587%25E6%25AC%25A0%25E9%2598%25BB%25E5%259A%2587%25E6%2580%25A7-%25E7%25BE%2585%25E8%2587%25B4%25E5%2585%2589-%25E8%258B%25A5-%25E5%25A4%25AA%25E8%25BE%25A3-%25E5%25B0%258F%25E4%25BC%2581%25E5%25AF%25A7%25E9%25A1%2598%25E4%25B8%258D%25E7%2594%25B3%25E8%25AB%258B%2F&d=pzZXWUTiTgu0UE2nVnCkCsg3oUHlS2gCMg1IFosJMKY%3D&h=33039d5d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%25E4%25BF%259D%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E6%25A5%25AD%25E8%25A8%2588%25E5%258A%2583-%25E5%2590%25A6%25E8%25AA%258D%25E7%25BD%25B0%25E5%2589%2587%25E6%25AC%25A0%25E9%2598%25BB%25E5%259A%2587%25E6%2580%25A7-%25E7%25BE%2585%25E8%2587%25B4%